{"tid":1867841,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"紅軍若奪英超即分400萬鎊獎金","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T11:14:06.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c41df459801a67eafe15bf9dba9b69dbcf149018","tid":1867841,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:28:36.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】只要利物浦今季贏得英超冠軍，一隊成員便將會獲得逾400萬鎊的獎金。<br />\n<br />\n目前利物浦已於英超積分榜上領先22分，據英國《鏡報》報道，只要該隊順利取得英超冠軍，一隊成員將會獲得超過400萬鎊冠軍獎金。現時利物浦已經英超25場不敗，當中只失了兩分暫得73分。<br />\n<br />\n在餘下13場比賽，只要他們可贏得6場便可取得球會第19個頂級聯賽冠軍，不止一吐多年烏氣，同時一洗多年被網民笑指「英超無冠」。英國傳媒已經指出，只要今季紅軍一線成員在英超上陣，都有份分全隊超過400萬鎊的獎金。<br />\n<br />\n據指獎金的多少取決於球員上陣次數，而球隊的常規正選便會獲得大約15萬鎊的獎金。在12月簽下新約的領隊高普，亦會因合約指明會因表現而調整工資，故高普勢贏不少獎金，名利雙收。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"18666100dae29a9ac141260f03bf5ddb1f27f5c6","tid":1867841,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/cfacc50f69745c744aec892f717bc0eb/2c6eff8f826ed936-a9/s1280x1920/ada238f545908cc83e869e9c7d3d92b8cc358177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2Fcfacc50f69745c744aec892f717bc0eb%2F2c6eff8f826ed936-a9%2Fs1280x1920%2Fada238f545908cc83e869e9c7d3d92b8cc358177.jpg&h=afc50926&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我利然硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce93ef6030489932e16f1f7742fb6774ef1079d3","tid":1867841,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:30:06.000Z","msg":"咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分比屋企隻狗？"},{"pid":"d7b87fe66fb582f03148aab862c80dd3fd5a478d","tid":1867841,"uid":19552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:30:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hEHBOjQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhEHBOjQ.png&h